        "title": {
          "type": "text",
          "$t": "Slovanský veľmožský dvorec"
        },
        "content": {
          "type": "html",
          "$t": "<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\nNáš spolupracovník Tomáš Humaj nakreslil pre našu stránku veľmi peknú a zároveň realistickú predstavu opevneného slovanského dvorca. Nejedná sa o žiaden konkrétny hrádok, ale vzhľad opevnenia, palisáda a zástavba sú veľmi realistické a opäť nám približujú život našich predkov v období 9. /10. storočia. &nbsp;</div>\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<br /></div>\n<div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\">\n<a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEg1Tp_94FPo-ZlQIePyDgVzQOcD0qRdhlF9Di2rDvlAf94wA5itV3bhECXQD8jwCssVrgNvYcUso8OJtmo7JXTxX2lJqjwHyNcUjC9LT1BVDwABrGwPuQK7TZuq4dQc_6RIL917wKoLv1E/s1600/PC126531.JPG\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEg1Tp_94FPo-ZlQIePyDgVzQOcD0qRdhlF9Di2rDvlAf94wA5itV3bhECXQD8jwCssVrgNvYcUso8OJtmo7JXTxX2lJqjwHyNcUjC9LT1BVDwABrGwPuQK7TZuq4dQc_6RIL917wKoLv1E/s1600/PC126531.JPG\" height=\"242\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<br />\n<div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\">\n<a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEhbnbzh9h8Jf_E_EoJbr8ztgILurncBnlzZ6OfJvh0-kDlNkEiUYa-0F4FtgnqEZ7LdlKWQiYNdhoG6Mc-pooR9lljhZ9357C_VTRnuoh3K-3OXz1dCPmhJxEy-U1BL4R8JegmNjOYwYYw/s1600/PC126532.JPG\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEhbnbzh9h8Jf_E_EoJbr8ztgILurncBnlzZ6OfJvh0-kDlNkEiUYa-0F4FtgnqEZ7LdlKWQiYNdhoG6Mc-pooR9lljhZ9357C_VTRnuoh3K-3OXz1dCPmhJxEy-U1BL4R8JegmNjOYwYYw/s1600/PC126532.JPG\" height=\"240\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<br />\n<div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\">\n<a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEhrDHLJlAA63e_U57PIzBGuZ_vV4WGjv3SCXcL54G4-qco17uDa9agZNH2SEr51pCR1R2YA9LQkN9iRKGMjW9PEivXuS7RSt9Ozpu2hamEAmi-d4J8b3JENFGnWcgunarLx2JybtzoD9uc/s1600/PC126534.JPG\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEhrDHLJlAA63e_U57PIzBGuZ_vV4WGjv3SCXcL54G4-qco17uDa9agZNH2SEr51pCR1R2YA9LQkN9iRKGMjW9PEivXuS7RSt9Ozpu2hamEAmi-d4J8b3JENFGnWcgunarLx2JybtzoD9uc/s1600/PC126534.JPG\" height=\"240\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<br />\n<div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\">\n<a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEg_5LsjIM5udcJqwQUq_AXZSXcLkSK_HkeLMJkV2cKfiy57ppZhH82wCYSshPxEWnOGgP7RrduhxH-L56HcqWyY8ztU-0S-IeZjUrR4EZF52hgAqJwrgrC98TOq0F6YHXTZoQiSK_kalR4/s1600/PC126535.JPG\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEg_5LsjIM5udcJqwQUq_AXZSXcLkSK_HkeLMJkV2cKfiy57ppZhH82wCYSshPxEWnOGgP7RrduhxH-L56HcqWyY8ztU-0S-IeZjUrR4EZF52hgAqJwrgrC98TOq0F6YHXTZoQiSK_kalR4/s1600/PC126535.JPG\" height=\"240\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<br />\n<div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\">\n<a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEjKIaKEZ5Y-GKZqp7xCu8JxOZRxkvwmXMShg0hY10eRlDNXYSXApJb-m44A1EgqeYFQavPkjSDQu1tZ-6JPHyupZb0hnxRlmtnf4qDAN2KurMlw8bvA7ixpsFbVeLddEQ1Nipl0hv5qKBc/s1600/PC126536.JPG\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEjKIaKEZ5Y-GKZqp7xCu8JxOZRxkvwmXMShg0hY10eRlDNXYSXApJb-m44A1EgqeYFQavPkjSDQu1tZ-6JPHyupZb0hnxRlmtnf4qDAN2KurMlw8bvA7ixpsFbVeLddEQ1Nipl0hv5qKBc/s1600/PC126536.JPG\" height=\"240\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<br /></div>\n"
